<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">经过岁月洗礼</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">他们用行动演绎</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">最浪漫的事就是陪你到老</span></strong></span></p>
